Package model_controllers

Class AppetizerModelController

java.lang.Object
model_controllers.AppetizerModelController
public class AppetizerModelController extends Object
Controller class for managing operations on the AppetizerModel objects, including adding, updating, deleting, and retrieving appetizers. This class interacts with the AppetizerModel to perform database operations and updates the ObservableList used by the View.
